            <span id="ChapterParagraphOne">
            <span id="BigFirstLetterText"></span>Another thing that attracted me to Kenneth and made him very dear to me was his testimony of the gospel. He set an example for his children in all aspects of the Church and what was important for us to do. He had served an honorable mission, and after we were married we always attended sacrament meeting, no matter how busy the farm work was. Mostly the farm was at a standstill on Sunday because we did not work on the Sabbath. We always paid tithing. He was a full-tithe payer. 

<br />
            </span>

