            <span id="ChapterParagraphOne">
            <span id="BigFirstLetterText"></span>One thing that I have always admired about Kenneth is that he was a very hard worker. He was always a good provider for our family. I was not under any pressure whatsoever to do anything that would be uncomfortable for me to do. I had a large home to take care of, and when the children began to come, my responsibility was to keep a home for our family. 


